523
00:31:13,373 --> 00:31:15,959
Honestly, Edie, I don't mind.

524
00:31:15,959 --> 00:31:19,963
You can skate off into the sunset
with Karl. Be my guest.

525
00:31:20,964 --> 00:31:23,175
That's good to know.

526
00:31:23,175 --> 00:31:26,970
