553
00:33:08,071 --> 00:33:12,075
Edie, come back here! We're not finished yet!

554
00:33:22,961 --> 00:33:26,465
It was an accident, Karl.
Edie knows it was an accident, right?

555
00:33:26,465 --> 00:33:28,467
